536
00:26:39,860 --> 00:26:41,580
我很想給大家看完

537
00:26:41,580 --> 00:26:43,380
我再講下去

538
00:26:47,100 --> 00:26:48,860
Good evening

539
00:26:48,860 --> 00:26:53,820
It's clear that the true problems of our nation

540
00:26:53,820 --> 00:26:55,940
are much deeper

541
00:26:55,940 --> 00:26:59,340
deeper than gasoline lines or energy shortages

542
00:26:59,340 --> 00:27:03,580
deeper even than inflation or recession

543
00:27:03,580 --> 00:27:08,060
In a nation that was proud of hard work

544
00:27:08,060 --> 00:27:10,300
strong families

545
00:27:10,300 --> 00:27:12,620
close-knit communities

546
00:27:12,620 --> 00:27:15,300
and our faith in God

547
00:27:15,300 --> 00:27:17,380
Too many of us now

548
00:27:17,380 --> 00:27:23,140
tend to worship self-indulgence and consumption

549
00:27:23,140 --> 00:27:25,380
Human identity

550
00:27:25,380 --> 00:27:30,980
is no longer defined by what one does

551
00:27:30,980 --> 00:27:36,380
but by what one owns

552
00:27:36,380 --> 00:27:38,100
But we've discovered

553
00:27:38,100 --> 00:27:42,620
that owning things and consuming things

554
00:27:42,620 --> 00:27:44,820
does not satisfy

555
00:27:44,820 --> 00:27:48,460
our longing for meaning

556
00:27:48,460 --> 00:27:52,180
We've learned that piling up material goods

557
00:27:52,180 --> 00:27:55,220
cannot fill the emptiness of lives

558
00:27:55,220 --> 00:28:00,180
which have no confidence or purpose

559
00:28:00,180 --> 00:28:05,140
This is not a message of happiness or reassurance

560
00:28:05,140 --> 00:28:07,780
but it is the truth

561
00:28:07,780 --> 00:28:11,420
and it is a warning

562
00:28:11,420 --> 00:28:13,700
沒錯,這個警告

563
00:28:13,700 --> 00:28:16,340
我相信到了今時今日

564
00:28:16,340 --> 00:28:22,660
比當時1976年更加真實

565
00:28:22,660 --> 00:28:24,180
我們都經歷過

566
00:28:24,180 --> 00:28:27,340
在2003年的時候

567
00:28:27,340 --> 00:28:29,540
有沙士

568
00:28:29,540 --> 00:28:32,220
在官方的報告當中

